articles.title: About me:
articles.description:
I am an Evolutionary Biologist and Social Psychologist (PhD from University of New South Wales, Sydney Australia). Currently a Data Analyst for the [Atlas of Living Australia](ala.org.au).

I am interested in understanding evolutionary and cultural underpinnings of human behaviour, in particular, sexist attitudes and behaviours.

Passionate about music. Love all genres, so love a good recommendation. I play piano sometimes.
